        <div id="content-area" class="clearfix">
            <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-block-4" class="block block-block blue block-odd block-1 first">
  <div class="block-inner">

                
		<div class="content" >
		  <p><img alt="" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/maritime-museum-of-the-atlantic.jpg" style="width: 376px; height: 180px;" /></p>
<h2>Maritime Museum of the Atlantic</h2>
<p>Located in the heart of Halifax’s waterfront, there’s no better place to immerse yourself in Nova Scotia’s rich maritime heritage than the Maritime Museum of the Atlantic.</p>
<p>From small craft boatbuilding to World War Convoys, the Days of Sail to the Age of Steam, the Titanic to the Halifax Explosion, you’ll discover the stories, events and people that have come to define Nova Scotia and its relationship with the sea.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/Events"><strong>Explore more Maritime Museum of the Atlantic events »</strong></a></strong></p>
<h2>Be social</h2>
<p><a href="https://twitter.com/ns_mma" target="_blank"><img alt="" class="not-responsive" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/nsm_twitter.jpg" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;" /></a> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/maritimemuseum" target="_blank"><img alt="" class="not-responsive" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/nsm_facebook.jpg" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;" /></a> <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/NovaScotiaMuseum" target="_blank"><img alt="" class="not-responsive" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/nsm_youtube.jpg" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;" /></a></p>
		</div>

  </div>
</div> <!-- /block-inner /block --><div id="block-views-display_block_content-block_2" class="block block-views block-even block-2">
