		<div class="content" >
		  <div class="view view-display-block-content view-id-display_block_content view-display-id-block_2 view-dom-id-b18f4029153bec836dd37e0a7dd03675">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div>
      
          <p><img alt="North from Nova Scotia" class="not-responsive cke-resize" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/may26_banner_ss_0.jpg" style="width: 173px; height: 206px;" /></p>
<h2>North from Nova Scotia on until November 6</h2>
<p>Our <a href="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/what-see-do/north-nova-scotia">special 2016 exhibit</a> explores a vital crossroads on land and at sea, where Nova Scotia, for thousands of years, connected people in the north to those in lands beyond.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
