		  <p><img alt="Google Map" class="not-responsive cke-resize cke-resize" src="https://maritimemuseum.novascotia.ca/sites/default/files/inline/images/google-maps-sqr.jpg" style="width: 173px; height: 173px;" /></p>
<h2>Google Maps Tour</h2>
<p>Tour the museum in Google Street View! Experience and explore our galleries and exhibits online to sample our marine history and stories that we share as Canada’s oldest and largest Maritime museum. <a href="https://www.google.ca/maps/@44.647774,-63.570978,3a,75y,243.47h,90.95t/data=!3m5!1e1!3m3!1sR-7dS8spsxx5eTR6VXupEQ!2e0!3e5">See the Google Maps Virtual Tour »</a></p>
